::Aerotaur::
       The second shot hits his body and his back arches upward into the air. 
 It lands again heavily on the ground and he doesn't move for a few moments.  
Suddenly he sits up panting.  He slowly steadies himself and rubs his back 
where there were still minor marks from the other shots.

       He looks up at Owlhawk and grins.  "Well that hurt like the Pit."  He 
stretches out his tense joints and pseudo-muscles.  He quickly scans the 
immediate area for Rodimus.  "What of Rodimus and Nightlight?"

--part1_195.18590303.2bc246a0_boundary
